    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """Mobile communications have evolved into a remarkable global service, achieving near-universal coverage with penetration rates close to 100% today. Socially, they have become an indispensable part of modern life, while economically, they serve as a critical enabler for businesses worldwide. LTE (Long-Term Evolution), the fourth generation (4G) of mobile technology, remains the most widely adopted wireless broadband standard globally. Although LTE continues to advance and will remain in use for years to come, the introduction of 5G New Radio (NR) marks the next step in meeting future connectivity demands.
While enhanced mobile broadband remains a primary goal, future wireless networks will also support a broader range of innovative applications. These include mission-critical communications, smart energy grids, autonomous vehicles and intelligent transportation systems, remote healthcare and telesurgery, and expanded industrial IoT, among others.
This course provides a clear and comprehensive understanding of current and next-generation mobile communication systems?particularly 4G-LTE and 5G-NR?with a focus on the Radio Access Network (RAN) and the Physical Layer (PHY). We will examine both technologies in parallel, exploring foundational concepts as well as the latest advancements."""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/antonio.perez%40upm.es> ;
    schema:inLanguage "Inglés"@es ;
    schema:instructor <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/angel.martinez.jimenez%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/antonio.perez%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/juan.moreno.garcia-loygorri%40upm.es> ;
    schema:name "Mobile Communication Systems"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/CB6> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CB6" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Poseer y comprender conocimientos que aporten una base u oportunidad de ser originales en el desarrollo y/o aplicación de ideas, a menudo en un contexto de investigación/ Students have demonstrated knowledge and understanding providing the groundwork or opportunity for innovation in developing and/or applying ideas, often within a research context"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/CB7> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CB7" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Que los estudiantes sepan aplicar los conocimientos adquiridos y su capacidad de resolución de problemas en entornos nuevos o poco conocidos dentro de contextos más amplios (o multidisciplinares) relacionados con su área de estudio/Students are capable of applying their knowledge, understanding, and problem"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/CB8> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CB8" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Que los estudiantes sean capaces de integrar conocimientos y enfrentarse a la complejidad de formular juicios a partir de una información que, siendo incompleta o limitada, incluya reflexiones sobre las responsabilidades sociales y éticas vinculadas a la aplicación de sus conocimientos y juicios/Students are capable of integrating knowledge and making complex decisions, which, although based on incomplete or limited information, require reflection on social and ethical responsibilities linked to the application of their knowledge and opinions"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/CEM03> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CEM03" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Analizar y diseñar la arquitectura, servicios y protocolos de la red de acceso radio de un sistema de comunicaciones móviles 4G y 5G / Analyze and design the architecture, services, and protocols of the radio access network in a 4G or 5G mobile communication system."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/CGI02> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CGI02" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Comprender el procedimiento, valor y límites del método científico, siendo capaz de identificar, localizar y obtenerdatos requeridos en un trabajo de investigación, de diseñar y guiar investigaciones analíticas, de modelado y experimentales, así como de evaluar datos de una manera crítica y extraer conclusiones. / Understand the procedure, value, and limits of the scientific method, being able to identify, locate and obtain data required in a research work, to design and guide analytical, modeling, and experimental investigations, as well as to critically evaluate data and extract conclusions."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/CGI03> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CGI03" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Valorar la importancia de las fuentes documentales, manejarlas y buscar la información para el desarrollo de cualquier trabajo de investigación. / Assess the importance of documentary sources, manage them and search for information for the development of any research work."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/CGI04> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CGI04" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Leer y comprender publicaciones dentro de su ámbito de estudio/investigación, así como su catalogación y valor científico. / Read and understand publications within their field of study / research, as well as their cataloging and scientific value."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/RA15> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA15" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Diseñar y desarrollar los componentes de una red de comunicaciones móviles y sus protocolos a partir de especificaciones técnicas/ Design and develop the components of a mobile communications network and its protocols based on technical specifications"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/RA2> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA2" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Aplicar el conocimiento adquirido a la comprensión de problemas cualitativos y cuantitativos relacionados con la codificación fuente y la codificación de canal/ Apply the knowledge acquired to the understanding of qualitative and quantitative problems related to source coding and channel coding"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/RA3> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA3" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Elegir los métodos y herramientas matemáticas necesarios para abordar la solución de un problema/ Choose the mathematical methods and tools necessary to tackle the solution of a problem"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/RA5> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA5" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Interpretar los datos derivados de observaciones empíricas y mediciones en términos de su importancia y relacionarlos con la teoría apropiada/ Interpret data derived from empirical observations and measurements in terms of their importance and relate them to the appropriate theory"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/RA7> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA7" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Aplicar el conocimiento adquirido a la solución de problemas cualitativos y cuantitativos relacionados con las comunicaciones móviles personales/ Apply the knowledge acquired to the solution of qualitative and quantitative problems related to personal mobile communications"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/RA8> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA8" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Identificar el impacto social y económico de las comunicaciones móviles en un contexto global/ Identify the social and economic impact of mobile communications in a global context."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/UPM1> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "UPM1" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Uso de la lengua inglesa / Use of the English language"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000602/2025-26/UPM4> a ns1:Competency ;
